data.description: Centrally Located Home, This Home has tile floors, ample bedrooms, and a Large Kitchen with stainless steel appliances; all the equipment is only one year old. Large living room and dining room area. Fenced property with front and back yards. Delightful Salt Water pool to enjoy with sunlight all day long. Plumbing was redone in 2021. The perfect home to enjoy with your family and entertain your friends; walking distance to Biscayne Blvd and Dixie Hwy business corridor with plenty of shops, supermarkets, and restaurants. Short drive to the beach and Highway access. Do not miss this opportunity; the Home has a lovely floor plan.
